About Tiew

Hi, this is Tiew Kee Hui reporting in! I'm currently an AI Engineer at Moneylion. I graduated from Multimedia University, Malaysia with a degree in Computer Science (specialization in Data Science)

I will be dedicating this blog for my tech experiences, projects, analysis and things I'm learning. Here is my resume if you are browing this website for recruitment.

Personality

My hobbies are reading about and exploring new technologies, playing video games and watching anime. I am a meticulous person and prefer to get things done as close to perfect as possible on the first try. I am mildly competitive but my main priority will always be self-improvement. What better way is there to improve than to challenge yourself, either by comparing yourself with others or with your past self?

I do think failing is good if you learn from it and only if you fail early so that the damage done is negligible. I am not fond of doing things during the eleventh hour anyway, so this blends well with my workflow.
